chroots - Simple chroot creating and maintenance
================================================

Chroots allow the creation of chroots by issue a setup command. It also allows
logging in to the chroots along with the necessary management of mount points. 

Installation
============

TBD

Basic work flow
===============

  chroots setup; # Create a chroot
  chroots init; # Mount the necessary dirs for proper chroot init
  chroots login; # Login into the chroot
